 you make changes to preview how it will look when you publish</div><textarea class=\"bpe_textarea\">**Live Preview**\nView your page preview as you make changes to preview how it will look when you publish</textarea><div class=\"bpe_textarea_mask\" style=\"display: none;\"></div><div class=\"format_mttri\" style=\"display: none;\"></div><div class=\"dropshipToolbarBottom clearfix\" style=\"display: none;\"><div class=\"format_first_block\"><div class=\"bpe_buttons\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_bold\" title=\"Bold\">Bold</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_ital\" title=\"Italic\">Italics</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_underline\" title=\"Underline\">Underline</a></div><span class=\"insertLinkToWebsite\">Link</span><div class=\"format_more\"><!-- --></div></div><div class=\"format_second_block\" style=\"display: none;\"><div class=\"format_less\"><!-- --></div><div class=\"bpe_buttons\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_strike\" title=\"Strikethough\">Strike</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_sub\" title=\"Subscript\">x<sub>y</sub></a><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_sup\" title=\"Superscript\">x<sup>y</sup></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"zonesEnd\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"CMS_Component_Obs ComponentCustom-Horizontal_Rule.tpl\" style=\"display: none;\"><div><div><div><a class=\"componentDelete\"></a><strong>Widget:</strong> Horizontal Rule</div></div></div></div><div class=\"el_p textareaWrapper\" data-level=\"\" data-el=\"p\" style=\"text-align: center; display: none;\"><div class=\"dragTextArea\"><!-- --></div><div class=\"visibleHighlight\">[See Full Feature List](/full-feature-list/)</div><textarea class=\"bpe_textarea\">[See Full Feature List](/full-feature-list/)</textarea><div class=\"bpe_textarea_mask\" style=\"display: none;\"></div><div class=\"format_mttri\" style=\"display: none;\"></div><div class=\"dropshipToolbarBottom clearfix\" style=\"display: none;\"><div class=\"format_first_block\"><div class=\"bpe_buttons\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"bpe_bold\" tit